This is a collection of scripts that interact with the Twitter API and OAuth. The
examples in this collection use Abraham's twitteroauth library by Abraham Williams,
the first PHP library for working with Twitter's OAuth API.

Demo: http://twitteroauth.labs.poseurtech.com/connect.php
Documentation: http://wiki.github.com/abraham/twitteroauth/documentation 
Source: http://github.com/abraham/twitteroauth
Twitter: http://dev.twitter.com